Extensible Web Document
==

* Cache system
* Template system
* Database abstraction layer
* Tree document model
* Module based document
* Ajax communication layer
* Javascript programming
* User auth system
* URL mapping
* Multiple document language
* Document statistics
* Menu construct
* Extensible module system

## Global documents ##

* Custom error pages
* Tags
* PDF
* Password protected
* Child document list

## Modules per document ##

* To Do list
* Downloads
* CSS Color extraction
* Images
* Text
* Events
* Element lists
* Code and highlighting
* RSS reader
* Search document
* Gallery
* Thumbnail linking from other documents
* Comment system
* Control panel for comment system
* Forms
* Meta information
* CSS style
* Access control
* Email suggest
* Calendar
* Notes

## Functions per module (all can be combined) ##

* Element lists
	* Links
	* Images
* Markdown

## Functions ##

Document layout
Date countdown